## Next Steps (For Project Owner)

To activate analytics on Vercel:
1. Deploy the project to Vercel (if not already deployed)
2. Navigate to the Analytics section in the Vercel dashboard
3. Click "Enable" to activate analytics for this project
4. After deployment, verify tracking by checking for Fetch/XHR requests to `/<unique-path>/view` in your browser's Network tab

